com.camerontec.catalys.server.collection

Class PersistentObject<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.camerontec.catalys.server.collection.PersistentObject<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The object type.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    IPersistentObject<T>

    public final class PersistentObject<T>
extends Object
implements IPersistentObject<T>
    IPersistentObject implementation that uses the Catalys collection registry.

    This class is part of the Catalys collections framework and is therefore HA aware. However, performance is degraded in HA context and this implementation makes no guarantees about how much performance degradation is incurred.

    By default in memory caching of the persistent object is enabled. To disable this use one of the constructors taking a java.util.Properties parameter with caching disabled (see CollectionProperties.IS_CACHING_ENABLED).

    See Also:
    ICollectionRegistry, CollectionProperties
